1. container folder convention:
/util for common util used in container
/m3958dir
  /config
  /data

2.all config copy from origin file, modify it in Dockerfile.

3.a service container may has config-vol, data-vol, log-vol

4. every service container use supervisord to start, default has dnsmasq started, you can read supervisord.conf.

5. container name conventions. 
service container: appname-servicename-service, for example: piwik-nginx-service
data container: appname-servicename-data-vol
log container: appname-servicename-log-vol
config container: appname-servicename-config-vol

6. web root path: /www/html

7. container debug run, default map /opt/dockerdata into /hostdir, so you can exchange file between host and container.

8. variable must use underscore, name use dash.
